FORRT Contributor Analyses

As of 20 August 2025, FORRT has a total of 90 completed or ongoing projects and support teams, with a total of 587 contributors. There is an average (mean) of 2.44 contributions per person across all FORRT projects, and the average number of contributors per project is 15.60.
